snippet.title: All Men Are Pigs - Full Game Release Trailer!
snippet.description:
All Men Are Pigs, a.k.a AMAP, has now been released as a full complete game as of June 15, and is available for sale at https://kaimakigames.itch.io/all-men-are-pigs

Navigate the crazy life at the island of Santa Locura while trying to get with the local hotties: Evandro, Olli, Diego, Stefanos, Deniz, Ram and Levon are fully available with fun and sexy romance routes!
